Name: Tanks in Labyrinth
About the game: Tanks in Labyrinth - is an cool indie game where you control a tank and fight against other players in a small labyrinth. The game has a lot of interesting bonuses: Hammer A hammer that destroys walls. Rocket Guided rocket. Machinegun A machine gun that can fire 20 bullets at once. Blast A bullet that explodes when the shot button is pressed again, or after a certain time. Wall A wall that can be put up, but after a while it will be destroyed. Portal Teleports to a random location.
